				<wikidot:authorName>Greenwake</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3157935</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't see anything interesting about this article. The SCP is a weird man that distracts people from committing suicide by making them angry at him. The log wasn't that funny to me but it looks like other people thought it was (humor really is subjective.) And if you're going to base your article's entire appeal on its humor then you might as well full sell it, and make it a joke SCP.</p> 
				 	]]>
