					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's a solid piece of flash fiction with a fun twist! I'm not sure what to make of the neutralization, though. Is this the first time a person's just straight-up killed an anomaly? Seems like the kind of thing that would have been done before, but there's something jarring about it. I don't know if it adds or detracts from the piece; it just kinda <em>happens</em> and I had to remark on it.</p> 
				 	]]>
